<DOCNO>WT22-B18-37</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA059-000320-B026-200</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.meteo.fr:80/connaitre/previ.html 137.129.254.112 19970114202724 text/html 6871
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 14 Jan 1997 20:27:23 GMT
