<HEAD><TITLE>METEO-FRANCE : AVISO</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY>
<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD WIDTH="550" ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=TOP>
<P><CENTER><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE WIDTH=225  HEIGHT=105 VSPACE=10 SRC="images/logo.gif"></CENTER>
