<H1><CENTER>AVISO VENT-FLUX :<BR>Data Base devoted to the study of the ocean-atmosphere interface</CENTER></H1>
<P>
<CENTER>Sorry for this incomplete English Version</CENTER></P>
<HR SIZE=5>
<A HREF="aviso_def_eng.html">AVISO vent-flux</A> offers a full range of meteorological data from Numerical Weather and Wave Prediction Models as well as from Conventional and Satellite observation relevant to the Ocean-Atmosphere interface. It also enables you to get processed products from these raw data.
<P>
<HR>

<H2>Data</H2>
<DL>
<DD><LI><A HREF="modele_eng.html">Model outputs</A>.<P> 
<DD><LI><A HREF="obs_ins_eng.html">Conventional observation</A> and <A HREF="obs_sat_eng.html">Satellite observation</A>.<P>
</DL>
<HR>

<H2>Products<IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 VSPACE=0 HSPACE=5 SRC="images/work.gif"></H2>
<DL>
<DD><LI><A HREF="prodbilan_eng.html">Monthly Global Statistics</A>.<P>
<DD><LI><A HREF="prodcoll_eng.html">Collocated data sets</A>.<P>
</DL>
<HR>

<H2>Toolbox<IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 VSPACE=0 HSPACE=5 SRC="images/work.gif"></H2>
<DL>
<DD><LI><A HREF="manip_don_eng.html">Data handling</A> and derived geophysical quantities.<P>
<DD><LI>Statistics et Graphics.<P>
</DL>
<HR>

<H2>Search our catalogue</H2>
<DL>
<DD><LI><A HREF="catalogue_eng.html">Available Data</A>.<P>
</DL>
<HR>

<H2><A HREF="commande_eng.html"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM VSPACE=0 HSPACE=5 SRC="images/mail.gif">To obtain data or products</A>.</H2>
<HR>

