<DOCNO>WT22-B18-101</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000326-B008-83</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.meteo.fr:80/connaitre/altocumulus.html 137.129.254.112 19970115000752 text/html 3348
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
