<H3> INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE CENTRE </H3>

</CENTER>
<HR SIZE=6>

<H3> <IMG align=middle SRC="http://www.meteo.fr/meteopol/images/cic.gif"> </H3>
<HR>
<DT>

<UL>
Meteo-France's International Conference Centre consists in an 280 seats amphitheater,
with simultaneous translation and video systems, meeting rooms from 25 to 75 seats, 
and a reception and exhibition area with adjoining offices. 
</UL>

