<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE> 8TH UNITREE USERS GROUP </TITLE>

</HEAD>
<BODY>

<CENTER>
<HR SIZE=6>
<H2>8TH UNITREE USERS GROUP MEETING </H2>
</CENTER>
<HR SIZE=6>
<HR>
<DL>
<DT>
This second part of the conference will begin at 14.00, on Wednesday November 13,
and will finish at 17.30 on Thursday, November 14.
</UL>
<HR>
<DL>
<DT>
This meeting will consist in : </UL>
<LI> reports by each Unitree vendors, describing Unitree status 
 and the future of the product for their company, </LI>
<LI> site reports : current Unitree users will explain how they use
the product and precise what they would like to see in the next releases
of Unitree.</LI> 
<LI> Unitree Inc. report, mainly focused on recent developments
around the product, </LI>
<LI> special Unitree or general HSM-related technical presentations, </LI>
<LI> a (closed) business meeting. </LI></UL>

So at this point in time we are also soliciting proposed presentations from
participating vendors and Unitree sites.
</UL>
<HR>
</BODY>

</HTML>
