<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Data : model outputs</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<H1><CENTER>Data : model outputs</CENTER></H1>
<HR SIZE 5>
<BR>
Model outputs archived in AVF result from following models :<P>

<B>Digital Models of weather forecast :<P></B>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="arpege_eng.html">ARPEGE model</A> (Action de Recherche Petite Echelle Grande Echelle) from M&eacute;t&eacute;o-France,<P>

<LI>IFS model (Integrated Forecast System) from ECMWF (European Center of Meteorological Weather Forecast).<P>
</UL>

<B>Digital Models of sea state forecast :</B><P>
<UL>
<LI>VAGAtla (the North Atlantic Ocean) and VAGMed (the west Mediterranean Sea) models from M&eacute;t&eacute;o-France,<P>

<LI>WAM (the Whole Globe) and WAMMed (the Mediterranean Sea) models from ECMWF.<P>
</UL>
<BR>
A number of climatological fields are available too, for example monthly climatology of surface water temperature. Others will be progressively developped and proposed by AVISO.
<P>

<HR>
