<TITLE>Monthly Global Statistics</TITLE>

<BODY>

<H1><CENTER>Monthly Global Statistics</CENTER></H1>

<HR SIZE=5> 

<BR>

<H2>Processing</H2> 

To authenticate basis data, we make systematically a set of monthly statistical products on geophysical parameters (wind, flux, radiation), as well as energizing and hybrid balance sheets.<P>

These tools are associate with production of "quick look".<P>

<H2>Quick Look</H2>

<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD WIDTH="350" ALIGN="center" VALIGN="top">
