<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Aviso : Toolbox</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<H1><CENTER>Aviso : Toolbox</CENTER></H1> 

<HR SIZE=5> 

<BR>

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=6 SRC="images/tools.xbm">Aviso system admits a set of processing tools, allowing to compute personal fields for each client.<P>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<H2>Client will able to choose :</H2>

<UL>
<LI>Parameter(s) to study,<P>
<LI>Processing type to execute,<P>
<LI>Scope definition,<P>
<LI>Spatial resolution,<P>
<LI>Temporal cover and resolution.<P>
</UL>

<BR>
<BR>
<H2>Tools list :</H2>

<UL>
<LI>Spatiotemporal extraction,<P>

<LI>Spatiotemporal interpolation : grid points --&gt; given point,<P>

<LI>Spatiotemporal colocation,<P>

<LI>Spatiotemporal statistics (mean values, minimal value, maximal value, standard deviations, histograms),<P>

<LI>Hybrid balance sheet computation,<P>

<LI>Heat balance sheet computation at surface water,<P>

<LI>Computation of difference in relation to climatology,<P>

<LI>Divergence computation,<P>

<LI>Rotational computation of wind,<P>

<LI>Neutral formulation stress,<P>

<LI>Developed formulation stress,<P>

<LI>Ekmann's transport,<P>

<LI>Ekmann's pumping computation,<P>

<LI>Computation of sensitive and latent heat flux (Large and Pond's formula),<P>

<LI>ERS orbit reconstitution,<P>

<LI>Dry tropospherical correction,<P>

<LI>Damp tropospherical correction,<P>

<LI>IR radiation flux (Berliand's formula),<P>

<LI>Solar flux,<P>

<LI>Wind fields reanalysis,<P>

<LI>Difference in difference to climatology,<P>

<LI>Unidimensional structure function,<P>

<LI>Bidimensional structure function,<P>

<LI>Tracks of obtained data (curves, isolines, vectors, orbits, histograms).<P>
</UL>

<HR>

<A HREF="index_eng.html"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=25 HSPACE=5 SRC="images/aviso2.gif">Back to AVISO Home Page</A>
<HR>
<A HREF="http://www.meteo.fr/e_index.html">
<IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE WIDTH=43 HEIGHT=43 SRC="/icons/meteo.gif">
