http://www.meteo.fr:80/perso/eric.sevault/Fortran2html/readme_4_0.html 137.129.254.112 19970115023848 text/html 14779
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 02:38:37 GMT
