<p><strong>I thought I was going to get blown away. And I couldn't believe
this was our country doing this to its citizens ...
I didn't see until after the retreat. When I read what was on
the backs of their clothes, I couldn't believe it.</strong><br>
-- Branch Davidian and former police officer Kevin Whitecliff, at his
June 1994 sentencing</p>

