<head>
<title>Controlling Your Own Body</title>
</head>

<body>

<center><a href="http://www.scimitar.com/">
<img src="/revolution/sponsors/scimitar.gif"
alt="SCIMITAR Internet Services"></a></center>

<h1>Controlling Your Own Body</h1>

<p>Libertarians believe you should have control over your own body. Although
this seems obvious, all other political groups want to control what substances
you can put into your body, what you can take out of it, how you maintain it
and what you and other consenting people do with it.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="repro/">Reproductive and sexual freedom</a></li>
<li><a href="drugs/">Recreational drugs</a></li>
<li><a href="health/">Health care</a></li>
