<head>
<title>Sexual Freedom</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Sexual and Reproductive Freedom</h1>

<p>Reproductive (or sexual) freedom covers many issues, including birth
control, sexual preference, abortion and forced sterilization. Libertarians
are divided on the abortion issue (depends on whether one considers the fetus
an individual); the Libertarian Party platform is pro-choice.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="china.html">China's brutal one-child policy</a></li>
<li><a href="nevada.html">Legal prostitution in Nevada</a></li>
