	February 1996: Internet censorship bill prohibits discussion
	of abortion</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/express/sex/">Nudity, obscenity
	and pornography</a></li>
<li><a href="quotes.html">Quotes</a></li>
<li><a href="online.html">Online resources</a></li>
</ul>

