<title>Law Enforcement</title>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Law Enforcement</h1>

<p>As the federal government asserts more and more control over every aspect
of its citizens' lives, our country is rapidly becoming the United Police
States of America. This document contains information relating to police
authority and police actions.</p>

<ul>
<li>Police abuses
	<ul>
	<li><a href="/revolution/multi/war/wtc.html">
		FBI implicated in World Trade Center bombing</a>
