	<ul>
	<li><a href="filming.html">Court rejects filming searches</a>
	</ul>
<li>Broadening of police powers
	<ul>
	<li><a href="terror95.html">1996 Counterterrorism Act a terror</a>
	</ul>
<li>Identification
	<ul>
	<li><a href="ca_id.html">California rules police may require ID</a>
	<li><a href="brownvtx.html">Supreme Court rules police can't
		require ID</a>
	<li><a href="healthid.html">Clinton considers health care ID card</a>
	<li><a href="uscard.html">U.S. agencies propose national ID card</a>
	<li><a href="greek_id.html">Greece considers adding religion to ID
		cards</a>
	<li><img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.cpsr.org/cpsr/privacy/ssn/html/privacy.html">CPSR's
