<h1>The Advance of the Libertarian Party</h1>

<p>The Libertarian Party kicks butt. Here's proof.</p>

<ul>
<li><p>The <a href="/revolution/by_name/L/LPUS.html">Libertarian Party</a>
has a web site including documents such as the Party Platform and news
releases; e-mail directories for national, state and local party officials;
brochures and more</p>

<li><p><a href="election/">Campaigns and elections</a> (including
presidential races)</p>

