<head>
<title>Science and Technology</title>
</head>
<body>

<center><a href="http://www.scimitar.com/">
<img src="/revolution/sponsors/scimitar.gif"
alt="SCIMITAR Internet Services"></a></center>

<h1>Science and Technology</h1>

<ul>
<li><a href="policy/">Science policy</a>
<li><A href="/revolution/science/enviro/">The environment</a></li>
<li>Regulation
	<ul>
	<li><a href="lacey.html">Transporting bugs across state lines</a></li>
	<li><A href="stevia.html">FDA bans natural sweetener</a></li>
	</ul>
<li>Revolutions in science
	<ul>
