<title>Environment</title>
</head>

<body>
<center><a href="http://www.scimitar.com/">
<img src="/revolution/sponsors/scimitar.gif"
alt="SCIMITAR Internet Services"></a></center>

<h1>The Environment</h1>

<p>1960's: overpopulation is destroying the planet (the sky is falling!).<br>
1970's: global cooling is destroying the planet (the sky is falling!).<br>
1980's: global warming is destroying the planet (the sky is falling!).<br>
1990's: ozone depletion is destroying the planet (the sky is falling!).</p>

<p>The sky is not falling.</p>

<p>Contents:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="pessimism.html">False pessimism</a></li>
<li><a href="wetlands.html">Wetlands</a></li>
<li><a href="science.html">The politicization of science</a></li>
<li><a href="gila.html">Feds want to poison Gila National Forest</a></li>
<li><a href="county.html">New Mexico county fights feds</a></li>
<li><a href="private.html">Property rights-based preservation groups</a></li>
<li><a href="humor/">Humor</a></li>
<li><a href="books.html">Books</a></li>
</ul>

