http://www.scimitar.com:80/kaleidosound/blues/fuller.html 198.69.72.176 19970215100126 text/html 3703
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 10:01:23 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 3532
Last-modified: Sat, 14 Sep 1996 04:24:02 GMT
