<body>

<h1>The French Revolution</h1>

<p>For the bicentennial of the French Revolution, <cite>The Freeman</cite>
published a <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
href="http://www.self-gov.org/freeman/8908pete.htm">commentary
on the American and French Revolutions</a>, essentially arguing that
the French Revolution ended in tyranny as a result of boneheaded economic
policies before it and at its start.</p>

