<body>

<h1>Malcolm X</h1>

<p>Malcolm X was a activist for black rights and self-defense in the 1960's.
He adopted an "X" in place of his last name to reject the name of the people
who owned his ancestors as slaves.</p>

<p>Appearances in <b>Revolution</b>:</p>
