<head>
<title>Reaction to Waco</title>
<!-- Place: USA -->
<!-- Time: February 28, 1993 - present -->
</head>

<body>

<h1>Reactions to Waco</h1>

<p>The federal government's 
<a href="/revolution/firearms/enforce/waco/">attack on the
Branch Davidians</a> at Waco, Texas in 1993 stirred a
wave of antigovernment sentiment. Of course, the government's own reaction
has generally been continued persecution.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="tribune-herald.html">March 1993: Waco newspaper flooded with
	antigovernment commentary</a></li>
<li><a href="irs.html">December 1993: IRS harasses surviving Davidians</a></li>
<li><a href="lptx.html">March 1993 - February 1995: Libertarian Party of
	Texas protests government actions</a></li>
<li><a href="/revolution/legal/corrupt/foster.html">July 1993:
	Vince Foster commits suicide</a>, wife says he was depressed
	over his role in Waco</li>
<li><a href="rehired.html">September 1993 - January 1994: Two BATF agents
	blamed for disaster, fired, then rehired</a></li>
<li><a href="marker.html">1994: Slain agents honored with marker</a></li>
<li><a href="elections.html">November 1994: Waco affects national
	elections</a></li>
<li><a href="tree.html">February, April 1995: Survivors plant trees in
	honor of dead</a></li>
<li><a href="cwj_protest.html">February 1995: Committee for Waco Justice
	protests at BATF headquarters</a></li>
<li><a href="signs.html">April 1995: Police steal signs at ongoing Waco
	protest in D.C.</a></li>
<li><a href="prison.html">May 1995: Imprisoned Davidian tells of
	torture</a></li>
<li><a href="hearings.html">July - November 1995: U.S Congress holds hearings on
	BATF/FBI actions at Waco</a></li>
<li><a href="suicide.html">July 1996: ATF agent commits suicide over
	Waco role</a></li>
</ul>

<p>The Waco massacre spurred growth in the <a
href="/revolution/firearms/militia/">citizen militia</a> movement.</p>

<p>Several terrorist acts may have been linked to Waco:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/revolution/multi/war/okc/">the April 1995 Oklahoma City
	federal building bombing</a> occurred on the Waco fire's
	second anniversary</li>
<li><a href="/revolution/multi/war/amtrak.html">the October 1995
	Amtrak derailment</a> involved a note referring to Waco</li>
<li><a href="/revolution/multi/war/flushing.html">the October 1995
	La Guardia bombing</a> also involved a note referring to Waco</li>
</ul>

