http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/community/educate/sepschool.html 198.69.72.176 19970215102920 text/html 5189
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 10:29:26 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
