Individual Liberty</a></li>

<li><img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
href="http://www.cais.com/agm/">Abortion Rights Activist</a></li>

<li><img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
href="http://www.cris.com/~bwjass/lfl/">Libertarians for Life</a></li>
</ul>

