<head>
<title>Immorality of Drug Prohibition</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Immorality of Drug Prohibition</h1>

<p>Prohibition of recreational drugs is morally wrong. Far from a noble cause,
drug prohibition has its roots in <a href="bigotry.html">bigotry and
hatred</a>. Prohibition is a <a href="rights.html">violation of individual
rights</a>.</p>

<p>While prohibition of drug use is wrong, that does not affect whether drug
use is itself right or wrong. It means, rather, that drug use is a moral
decision made by the individual without the threat of force.</p>

<hr><p align=center><font size=-1 color="#990000">
<a href="/revolution/">Topics</a> -
<a href="/revolution/by_place/">Places</a> -
<a href="/revolution/by_time/">Times</a> -
