<DOCHDR>
http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/firearms/crime/protect.html 198.69.72.176 19970215110821 text/html 22462
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 15 Feb 1997 11:08:07 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 22290
Last-modified: Thu, 31 Oct 1996 22:44:40 GMT
