<head>
<title>Self-defense</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Self-defense</h1>

<p>Opponents of the right to self defense often claim that firearms are not
good defensive weapons. These cases bear witness otherwise. While other
documents seek to give arguments and statistics to back up gun rights,
this one consists entirely of real-world examples of self defense. Most
involve firearms, a few involve other weapons.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="jun1993/">June 1993</a>: victim kills stalker</li>
<li><a href="mar1994/">March 1994</a>: robbers routed; cougar stopped; ...</li>
<li><a href="apr1995/">April 1995</a>: intruder scared</li>
<li><a href="may1995/">May 1995</a>: thugs repelled; attackers killed; ...</li>
<li><a href="jun1995/">June 1995</a>: intruder scared; fugitive shot; ...</li>
<li><a href="jul1995/">July 1995</a>: carjacker killed; self-defender
	arrested</li>
<li><a href="phoenix.html">Drive-bys in Phoenix</a></li>
</ul>

