<head>
<title>Requiring Firearms Ownership</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Communities Requiring Gun Ownership</h1>

<p>Several communities have passed symbolic ordinances requiring the
ownership of firearms, as a statement of opposition to gun control. The
list below is by no means complete.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="us/me/bowerbank.html">Bowerbank, Maine</a>
<li>Catron County, New Mexico
<li><a href="us/ga/kennesaw.html">Kennesaw, Georgia</a>
</ul>

