<head>
<title>Moderns on Self-Defense</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Modern Thinkers on Self-Defense</h1>

<hr>

<p>Among the many misdeeds of the <a
href="/revolution/by_place/Europe/UK/">British</a> rule in
<A href="/revolution/by_place/Asia/India/">India</a>, history
will look upon the act of depriving a whole nation of arms, as the blackest.</p>

<p>-- Mahatma Gandhi, in his <cite>Autobiography</cite>, p. 446
(unverified)</p>

<hr>

<hr><p align=center><font size=-1 color="#990000">
