<head>
<title>NRA</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>NRA</h1>

<p>The National Rifle Association (NRA) of America is a gun owner's
organization. The NRA promotes sporting and self-defense uses of firearms.
The NRA is an active player in U.S. politics.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
1600 Rhode Island Ave. NW, Washington, DC 20036<br>
Phone: 202-828-6000<br>
File archives: <img src="/images/ftp.gif" alt="[FTP]"><a
	href="ftp://ftp.nra.org/">ftp.nra.org</a><br>
Web: <img src="/images/www.gif" alt="[WWW]"><a
	href="http://www.nra.org/">http://www.nra.org</a><br>
Gopher: <img src="/images/gopher.gif" alt="[GOPHER]"><a
	href="gopher://gopher.nra.org">gopher.nra.org</a><br>
WAIS: <a href="wais://wais.nra.org/">wais.nra.org</a><br>
Mailing lists: send the word help as the body of a message to <img
	src="/images/mail.gif" alt="[EMAIL]"><a
	href="mailto:listproc@nra.org">listproc@NRA.org</a><br>
NRA-ILA GUN-TALK BBS: (703) 934-2121<br>
</address>

