<head>
<title>Self-Defense Network</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Self-Defense Network</h1>

<p>The Self-Defense Network (SDN) was a mailing list for reporting
incidents of self-defense using firearms. It now appears to be
defunct.</p>

