<head>
<title>JPFO</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Jews for the Protection of Firearms Ownership</h1>

<p>Jews for the Protection of Firearms Ownership (JPFO) is a pro-gun rights
group that supports firearm ownership as a defense against possible tyranny.</p>

<p>Contact:</p>
<address>
Dept. GA, 2872 S. Wentworth Ave., Milwaukee, WI 53207<br>
voice: (414) 769-0760<br>
</address>

