<DOCHDR>
http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/body/drugs/usage/ 198.69.72.176 19970216051052 text/html 6414
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 05:11:08 GMT
