<DOCHDR>
http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/body/drugs/users/ 198.69.72.176 19970216051059 text/html 7739
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 05:11:18 GMT
