<h1>Drug Humor</h1>

<hr>

<h2>Time</h2>

<p>Two dudes on acid are sitting on a curb. A fire engine, with lights and
sirens blaring, goes flying by.</p>

<p>One dude says to the other, "Man, I thought he'd never leave."</p>

<hr>

<h2>Advocacy</h2>

<p>I hate to advocate drugs, alcohol, violence, or insanity to 
anyone, but they've always worked for me.</p>
<p>-- Hunter S. Thompson</p>

