http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/body/drugs/morals.html 198.69.72.176 19970216051248 text/html 10311
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 05:13:01 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 10139
Last-modified: Thu, 31 Oct 1996 22:43:23 GMT
