http://www.scimitar.com:80/revolution/by_topic/body/health/insurance.html 198.69.72.176 19970216051306 text/html 8529
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 05:13:25 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
