<p> <a name=fn29>29.</a> "The Effects of Managed Care on Use and Costs of Health
Services," CBO Staff Memorandum, (Washington: Congressional Budget Office, June
1992).</p>

<p> <a name=fn30>30.</a> Study: "Managed Care No Cost Cure-All," <cite>Atlanta
Constitution</cite>, May 12, 1993.</p>

<p> <a name=fn31>31.</a> Alain Enthoven, "Health Plan, The Only Practical
Solution to the Soaring Cost of Medical Care," 1980.</p>

