<p> <a name=fn35>35.</a> Id.</p>

<p> <a name=fn36>36.</a> See e.g., Rooney, "Give Employees Medical IRA's and
Watch Costs Fall," <cite>Wall Street Journal</cite>, January 22, 1992.</p>

<p> <a name=fn37>37.</a> Based on claims experience in
<a href="/revolution/by_place/NorthAmerica/USA/il/Chicago.html">Chicago</a>,
one of the
nation's highest cost areas. In more typical areas, about 9% of claims exceed
$2,000.  Based on claims distribution analysis by Tillinghast corporation.</p>

